Direct the employees with loans amortization paid by the LGU to reimburse the said payments either by paying cash or deducting from their salaries or other remunerations immediately;

Require those officials and employees who are already separated from the service to settle/liquidate their outstanding obligations by sending demand letters. Copy of the said demand letters bearing the receipts of the concerned accountable officials/employees should be furnished the Audit Team;

Conduct regular monitoring and analysis of receivable accounts to ensure that these are collected when these become due and demandable and that cash advances are liquidated within the prescribed period depending upon their nature and purpose; and

Prepare all the reports required by COA Circular No. 2016-005 and request the write off of the dormant receivable accounts.

